Terms & Conditions

Last updated: October 9, 2024

  Welcome to the Eny app. By downloading or using this application, you agree to these Terms & Conditions. Please read them carefully before using the app. If you do not agree to these terms, you must stop using the app.

1. Acceptance of Terms
  By using the Eny application, you agree to comply with these Terms & Conditions. These terms may be modified at any time, and it is your responsibility to regularly review them to stay informed of any changes.

2. Use of the Application
  Eny is an application that collects location data to optimize solar irradiation calculations and assist you in solar system sizing. By using this application:

    -  You agree to provide accurate and up-to-date information.
    -  You must not use the app for illegal or unauthorized purposes.
    -  You must respect the rights of others, including their privacy.

3. Data Collection and Use
  To improve the user experience, Eny collects certain information, including:

  Location Data: Used to enhance solar irradiation calculations.
  Personal Data (name, email address, photo): Used solely for identification purposes and never shared without your explicit consent.
  The use of this data is governed by our Privacy Policy, which you must read and accept.

