  The use of the Eny app is at your own risk. We do not guarantee that the app will function without interruptions or errors. While we strive to maintain accurate and up-to-date information, Eny cannot be held responsible for any errors or omissions in the information provided.

  We will not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting from the use or inability to use the application.

6. Modifications and Termination
  We reserve the right to modify or temporarily or permanently suspend any part of the Eny application without prior notice and without liability. We also reserve the right to terminate your access to the app at any time if you fail to comply with these Terms & Conditions.

7. Your Obligations
  As a user of the Eny app, you agree to:

    -  Not alter or harm the application in any way.
    -  Provide accurate information and not impersonate others.
    -  Comply with the laws in force when using the application.
8. Governing Law and Jurisdiction
  These Terms & Conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws in force. Any dispute related to the use of the application will be subject to the jurisdiction of competent courts.

9. Contact
  If you have any questions or concerns regarding these Terms & Conditions, please contact us at: eny.solar000@gmail.com.
